No. 09-758 (R46-021). Elouise Pepion Cobell, et al., Petitioners v. Ken L. Salazar, Secretary of the Interior, et al. 561 U.S. 1020, 130 S. Ct. 3497,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1085,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5260. June 24, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 573 F.3d 808.
